            . I am street-keeper. On the 24th of November I was in <placeName id="t18251208-148-crimeloc771">High-street, St. Giles'</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18251208-148-crimeloc771" type="placeName" value="High-street, St. Giles'"></interp>
